      <p class="text-left fs-6"><%= image_tag "aura_logo_v6_512.png", class: "rounded float-start", alt: "Aura Weather", style: "width: 100px; margin-top: 25px;" %>
        <u class="fs-2">Aura Weather Forecaster</u><br/>
        Aura Weather delivers accurate and fast weather forecasts using NOAA and other trusted sources.
        Designed with simplicity and performance in mind, Aura Weather gives you current conditions, radar imagery,
