          <li> Tap short forecast to see the days' forecast</li>
          <li> Tap paint palette to cycle themes</li>
          <li> 72 Hours of hourly info including Wind, Rain, Humidity and Dew point</li>
          <li> User History to find recently searched forecasts</li>
          <li> Pin a forecast, press the cloud and make it sunny</li>
          <li> Pinned forecasts show on home page</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
